Comus stood looking at the portrait of his mother with the feeling of one who comes suddenly across a once familiar half forgotten acquaintance in unfamiliar surroundings . 
The likeness was undoubtedly a good one , but the artist had caught an expression in Francesca's eyes which few people had ever seen there . 
