Michael boded bad news , but at any rate news , and she gave him an almost cordial welcome . 
Well , you see I wasn't far wrong about Miss de Frey and Courtenay Youghal , was I ? he chirruped , almost before he had seated himself . 
Francesca was to be spared any further spinning out of her period of uncertainty . 
Yes , it's officially given out , he went on , and it's to appear in the MORNING POST to morrow . 
I heard it from Colonel Deel this morning , and he had it direct from Youghal himself . 
Yes , please , one lump I'm not fashionable , you see . 
He had made the same remark about the sugar in his tea with unfailing regularity for at least thirty years . 
